607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBeefd6de5" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"item=
scope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !im=
portant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bot=
tom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> Aug. 16 filing</a> was =E2=80=
=A6=C2=A0a reminder that Cohen owned the stock? In March, <a href=3D"https:=
//link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/28895329.263565/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2V=
jLmdvdi9BcmNoaXZlcy9lZGdhci9kYXRhLzg4NjE1OC8wMDAxMTkzODA1MjIwMDA0MjYvc2MxM2=
QxMzM1MTAwMl8wMzA3MjAyMi5odG0/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB94731958" itemprop=
=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #0=
00000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-b=
ottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">=
 Cohen reported</a> that he owned about 9.45 million shares (via direct sto=
ck ownership and high-strike January 2023 options), or about 9.8% of the co=
mpany; later that month, <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com=
/click/28895329.263565/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9BcmNoaXZlcy9lZGdhci9kYXRh=
Lzg4NjE1OC8wMDAwOTIxODk1MjIwMDA5NzIvc2MxM2RhMTEzMzUxMDAyXzAzMjQyMDIyLmh0bQ/=
607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB5361407e" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"item=
scope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !im=
portant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bot=
tom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> he reported</a> that he had rea=
ched an agreement with Bed Bath on the appointment of new directors. Nothin=
g changed since then except that Bed Bath bought back some stock, meaning t=
hat Cohen=E2=80=99s 9.45 million shares now represented 11.8% of the compan=
y. So he <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/28895329.=
263565/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9BcmNoaXZlcy9lZGdhci9kYXRhLzg4NjE1OC8wMDAx=
