<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">What <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbus=
iness.com/click/28895329.263565/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZnQuY29tL2NvbnRlbnQvNTQwNTY=
3ZWMtNjZiOS00ODU4LWJiZTgtOTgyZTY0M2MxNmZh/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB0e2dd2fb=
" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D=
"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px=
; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-colo=
r: #ccc;"> a terrible job</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Morgan Stanley has ordered an internal lawyer =
to shadow the unit entangled in a federal investigation into block trading,=
 underscoring the gravity of the probe and the steps the lender is taking t=
o beef up supervision.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The Wall Street bank has embedded one of its l=
awyers to sit on its US equity syndicate desk to supervise bankers and answ=
er their legal questions, according to people briefed on the arrangement. .=
..</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">It is the latest example of the fallout from t=
he investigations by the Department of Justice and Securities and Exchange =
Commission into Morgan Stanley=E2=80=99s block trading business, which gath=
ered momentum after the collapse last year of Bill Hwang=E2=80=99s Archegos=
 Capital Management. =E2=80=A6 Heightened scrutiny of block trading has eme=
rged as one of the main legal risks faced by Wall Street groups, alongside =
a separate investigation into bankers=E2=80=99 use of personal mobile phone=
s to communicate with clients and counterparties.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">We have <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomberg=
business.com/click/28895329.263565/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGlu=
aW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMDItMTYvcGVvcGxlLWFyZS13b3JyaWVkLWFib3V0LWJsb2NrLXR=
yYWRlcz9jbXBpZD1CQkQwODMwMjJfTU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVtYWlsJnV0bV9zb3=
VyY2U9bmV3c2xldHRlciZ1dG1fdGVybT0yMjA4MzAmdXRtX2NhbXBhaWduPW1vbmV5c3R1ZmY/6=
07f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB18eb7b4a" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"items=
cope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !imp=
ortant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bott=
om-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  talked</a> about the <a href=3D=
"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/28895329.263565/aHR0cHM6Ly93=
d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMDMtMjgvYmFyY2xheXMtc29=
sZC10b28tbWFueS1ub3Rlcz9jbXBpZD1CQkQwODMwMjJfTU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1dG1fbWVkaXVtPW=
VtYWlsJnV0bV9zb3VyY2U9bmV3c2xldHRlciZ1dG1fdGVybT0yMjA4MzAmdXRtX2NhbXBhaWduP=
W1vbmV5c3R1ZmY/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB93dd72c5" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" it=
emscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decor=
ation: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000=
000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  block-trade</a>=
 probe <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/28895329.26=
3565/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMDMtMz=
EvdGhlLXNlYy1pcy1jb21pbmctZm9yLXNwYWNzP2NtcGlkPUJCRDA4MzAyMl9NT05FWVNUVUZGJ=
nV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTIyMDgzMCZ1=
dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249bW9uZXlzdHVmZg/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB4b24c378" itemprop=
=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #0=
00000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-b=
ottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">=
  before</a>.=C2=A0The equity syndicate desk is in the uncomfortable positi=
on of talking to (1) investors, about what stocks they would like to buy, a=
nd (2) public companies and big shareholders, about selling their stocks. B=
roadly speaking, if Morgan Stanley is buying a block of stock from a big se=
ller after the close today and then re-selling it to its investor clients, =
the syndicate desk can=E2=80=99t go around calling those investor clients t=
o say =E2=80=9CHey a block of XYZ stock is coming after the close, get read=
y.=E2=80=9D That would be bad. But if it is chatting with those investor cl=
ients all day, can it say =E2=80=A6=C2=A0=E2=80=9CBusy day today guys=E2=80=
=9D? =E2=80=9CStick around after the close today, we=E2=80=99ve got a fun o=
ne for you=E2=80=9D? =E2=80=9CHow are you feeling about entertainment compa=
nies these days=E2=80=9D? Can it drop some hints? Can it use tone and body =
language? Can the investors, who know the market well and have some idea of=
 what blocks might come loose, make an informed guess about what the syndic=
ate desk is talking about? Can the investors then position themselves by, f=
or instance, dumping some XYZ stock during the afternoon and then buying it=
 back at a discount after the close?</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Oh, I don=E2=80=99t know, I don=E2=80=99t want=
 to give you legal advice. But if you=E2=80=99re the Morgan Stanley lawyer =
who covers the syndicate desk, you do have to give the syndicate desk legal=
 advice. You have to give some sort of general answer to those questions. =
=E2=80=9CYou can talk to investors about broad sectors without disclosing t=
he name of the company that you have a block for,=E2=80=9D maybe, or whatev=
er, I don=E2=80=99t know. You make some rules and you hand the rules to the=
